{"tid":1280534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請聚焦中英聯合聲明!","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:18:15.000Z","uid":229777,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"770d579df045b23ae4c10c3e1ad4c38bd7e971de","tid":1280534,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"喺大部份國家眼中基本法係內政，而五大訴求亦只不過係我哋對港共嘅訴求，佢哋係無位入㗎<br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明先係UN落案國際條約呀，用呢個先可以有海外support<br />\n<br />\n就算你覺得英國唔做嘢，呢個仍然係壓力，亦可以俾位其他國家進埸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a011f665f9f637e90c5713556e54d65c56c9299f","tid":1280534,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"你叫楊on9收返「殘而不廢」先講啦"},{"pid":"29ed75648a73181369ee95b68d72e6a86bc26621","tid":1280534,"uid":224323,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"其實係，認真搞的話，目標一定係高舉「中英聯合聲明」。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗講咩基本法50年不變，<span style=\"color: red;\">只需要不停強調<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「中英」</span>兩個字就得。</span>"},{"pid":"5b0b1ad0addf818afd94ba6e182245417c493b3c","tid":1280534,"uid":224323,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"仲要用英文講，不停提「Sino-British Joint Declaration」。<br />\n<br />\n冇英屬香港經歷，何來今日。"},{"pid":"79f4acb2526e81430d650f2466d30ddd5a911995","tid":1280534,"uid":38381,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"外交部發言人陸慷: &lt;中英聯合聲明&gt;作為一個歷史文件，不再具有任何現實意義，對中央政府對香港特區的管理也不具備任何約束力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/101749/中國外交部-中英聯合聲明是歷史文件-不具任何現實意義及約束力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F101749%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%9